type.description:
Supported auth scheme. Mapping (authScheme → engine credential-type slug → OpenBao credential fields):
  • none    → (no auth)
  • basic   → http-basic-auth   → {username, password}
  • bearer  → http-bearer-token → {token}
  • api-key → http-header-auth  → {headerName, headerValue}
The credential VALUE lives in OpenBao under the tenant's credentialRef and is resolved server-side at call time (ADR-020 B.6, ADR-024).
